Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么能算家庭心理咨询呢\N{\fs38}How is this even family therapy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没叫上爸爸 外公又不来\N{\fs38}if Dad’s not invited and Grandpa won’t come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃个热狗又有什么勇不勇敢的\N{\fs38}Yeah, and what’s courageous about eating a hot dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人想来这儿 逼崽子们\N{\fs38}It’s nobody’s choice to be here, you knobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们的校长要求我们一家来做心理咨询\N{\fs38}The family was told to get counseling by your principal,
