Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在美术教室里吸陶釉\N{\fs38}huffing pottery glaze in the art room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者在历史课上尿了一桌子\N{\fs38}and desk wetting in history class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 Smith—家\N{\fs38}Oh, the Smith family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少了个爸爸\N{\fs38}minus a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也是王医生的病人吗\N{\fs38}You’re patients of Dr. Wong, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时而已 这是学校的要求\N{\fs38}Temporarily -- by order of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 你们吃了多久的大便了\N{\fs38}Me too. How long have you all been eating poop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 从来没\N{\fs38}We.. .have never.. .
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃过大便\N{\fs38}eaten poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我也没有\N{\fs38}Uh, me, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我的家人都到哪儿去了\N{\fs38}Say, where did my family get off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smith一家 我是王医生\N{\fs38}Smith family, I’m Dr. Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\fs38}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说还有个外公也会来加入我们\N{\fs38}I was told there was a grandpa that might be joining us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在忙一个实验 抽不开身\N{\fs38}He got wrapped up in an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个科学家\N{\fs38}He’s a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正经科学家 跨星系\N{\fs38}Like, legit, like on a an inter-galactic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科幻小说的那种水平 他的工作非常\N{\fs38}sci-fi level. His work is very--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把他自己变成了一根腌黄瓜\N{\fs38}He turned himself into a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你妈还在讲话 对不起\N{\fs38}Morty, Mom’s talking. I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这对于我们谈及家庭纪律问题\N{\fs38}I suppose that’s a good segue
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很好的过渡\N{\fs38}into our little discipline cases here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公会经常把自己变成腌黄瓜吗\N{\fs38}Does Grandpa turn himself into a pickle a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不会 这问的都什么问题\N{\fs38}What?! No! What kind of question is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问出来绝对不是用来攻击或伤害你的问题\N{\fs38}The kind that wasn’t designed to attack or hurt you in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢天哪 又来了\N{\fs38}Oh, Jesus Christ, one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我爸从来没把自己变成腌黄瓜过\N{\fs38}No, my father has never turned himself into a pickle before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他难以预料而且比较古怪\N{\fs38}He’s unpredictable and eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全家都是这样 说到这个\N{\fs38}The whole family is. Speaking of which...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那全家都来聊聊\N{\fs38}Okay, let’s open things up to the whole family,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容我问问这个问题\N{\fs38}and let me ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们觉得外公为什么要把自己变成一根腌黄瓜\N{\fs38}Why do we think Grandpa turned himself into a pickle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 恶\N{\fs38}Wow. Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这是你的地盘 不是我的\N{\fs38}Hey, listen, I know this is your world, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽快离开 就能尽快回去\N{\fs38}The sooner I can get out, the sooner I can go back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大泡拉屎 你也能继续吃屎维生了\N{\fs38}to taking big craps, and you can go back to subsisting on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是只卖力的老鼠\N{\fs38}You are one driven rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能再卖力一点吗\N{\fs38}Could you be a little more driven?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往右来点\N{\fs38}To the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好好\N{\fs38}Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快快 新鲜新鲜新鲜的\N{\fs38}Come on, come on, come on! Fresh, fresh, fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦哦哦 这是你们的朋友吗\N{\fs38}Whoa, whoa, whoa, was this your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别操心 他做着他钟爱的事死掉的 做一只蠢老鼠\N{\fs38}Don’t worry, he died doing what he loved,being a dumb fucking rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊\N{\fs38}Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说我爸是完美的\N{\fs38}I didn’t say my father is perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说他做的事很重要\N{\fs38}I said his work is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她所谓重要的事是\N{\fs38}And she’s saying what’s important is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公因为不想来而撒了谎\N{\fs38}that Grandpa lied to you to get out of coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 他才没\N{\fs38}Oh, he did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来做个实验\N{\fs38}Let’s do an experiment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你们家重视科学\N{\fs38}I get the impression this family values science.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你确信你知道\N{\fs38}So raise your hand if you feel certain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注射器里是什么 请举手\N{\fs38}you know what was in the syringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你确信你知道\N{\fs38}Raise your hand if you know for certain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注射器里没有抗腌黄瓜血清 请举手\N{\fs38}the syringe does not contain anti-pickle serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth 你的手刚刚动了一下\N{\fs38}Beth, your hand did a little thing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的看不出这是怎么回事吗\N{\fs38}Do you really not see what’s happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讲 - 王医生\N{\fs38}Tell me. -Well, Dr. Wong --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带说下 这名字种族歧视\N{\fs38}by the way, racist name --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显 Morty和Summer在利用\N{\fs38}obviously, Morty and Summer are seizing on your
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这莫名其妙执着于腌黄瓜这点\N{\fs38}arbitrary pickle obsession as an end run
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来避开本来是他们的心理治疗\N{\fs38}around what was supposed to be their therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 我觉得这个腌黄瓜的事\N{\fs38}Oh, I think this pickle incident
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比其他问题都更接近\N{\fs38}is a better path than any other
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们家庭失调的核心\N{\fs38}to the heart of your family’s dysfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为有可能你和你父亲的关系\N{\fs38}I think it’s possible that you and your father
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一种非常特别的心理动力驱动着\N{\fs38}have a very specific dynamic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为这种动力\N{\fs38}I don’t think it’s one
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不鼓励表达情感和脆弱\N{\fs38}that rewards emotion or vulnerability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表达这些可能会受到惩罚\N{\fs38}I think it may punish them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得它可能损害了你的婚姻\N{\fs38}I think it’s possible that dynamic eroded your marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且影响了你的孩子们 他们倾向于\N{\fs38}and is infecting your kids with a tendency
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们的情感发泄在别处\N{\fs38}to misdirect their feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚你丫的\N{\fs38}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈 - 妈\N{\fs38}Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩也滚丫的\N{\fs38}Fuck both of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 你可能也注意到了\N{\fs38}By the way, you might notice that in spite of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你有诸多显眼的特点\N{\fs38}your numerous distinctive features
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可没管你叫刀疤脸 条纹鼠 或者哥利亚这样的名字\N{\fs38}I never gave you a name like Scar or Stripe or Goliath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对我而言 你一点都不特别\N{\fs38}That’s because, to me, you aren’t special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这帮老鼠而言你很特别 但它们都死了\N{\fs38}You were special to rats. Now they’re dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜你本更应该来讨好我的\N{\fs38}I guess it was me you should have impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠 我太爱自己了\N{\fs38}God damn it, I love myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌黄瓜Rick\N{\fs38}Pickle Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑酷搞定 搞定\N{\fs38}Get that parkour. Get that parkour!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 淡定 我只是想找到最近的出口而已\N{\fs38}Hey, it’s cool.Just need to find the nearest exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哇哇 别慌啊你们\N{\fs38}Whoa, whoa, whoa! No need to freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这他妈到底是谁家的厕所啊\N{\fs38}Who in the fuck’s toilet is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是个什么东西\N{\fs38}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一根腌黄瓜 一只老鼠 二者皆是\N{\fs38}A pickle? A rat? Both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它说它是个科学家\N{\fs38}It says it’s a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在哪\N{\fs38}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像在用通风道\N{\fs38}It seems to be using the air ducts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟邮件管道到处乱窜\N{\fs38}and the mail tubes to get around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为它正在收集办公用品\N{\fs38}It’s been gathering office supplies, we think,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来造武器\N{\fs38}to build weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看看它在办公楼夹层干了什么好事\N{\fs38}But look what it did on the mezzanine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它把一个瓶子从不可回收桶扔到了可回收桶里\N{\fs38}It transferred a bottle from the trash to the recycling bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管这东西是啥 它都在羞辱我们\N{\fs38}Whatever this thing is, it’s shaming us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有三十四个全副武装的警卫 但是却杀不死一个腌黄瓜\N{\fs38}We have 34 armed guards, and we can’t kill a pickle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十二个全副武装的警卫\N{\fs38}32 armed guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他杀了两个\N{\fs38}He killed two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它打电话过来了\N{\fs38}It’s on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接起来 然后对他的电话进行定位\N{\fs38}Put him on, and locate the phone he’s using.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 你能不能 呃 麻烦让我出去\N{\fs38}Hi, urn, can you, uh please let me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你光是出现在这栋建筑里\N{\fs38}Your mere presence in this building
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就已经违反国际法了\N{\fs38}violates international law.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:12:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你没有杀那两个人我也不能让你离开\N{\fs38}I couldn’t let you out even if you hadn’t killed two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人算是自杀\N{\fs38}You should know those men killed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么讲\N{\fs38}PAVEL: And how is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不让我离开\N{\fs38}They didn’t let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Solen'ya\N{\fs38}Solen ‘ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 好好做你的事 他妈的小屁孩\N{\fs38}Shut your mouth and do your jobs,you fucking children!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 现在是不太方便说话吗还是\N{\fs38}Uh, is this not a good time or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的一些手下叫你"Solen'ya"\N{\fs38}Some of my men are calling you “Solen’ya” --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是腌黄瓜人 一个愚蠢的传说\N{\fs38}the Pickle Man, an old wives’ tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会从冷掉的汤里爬出来\N{\fs38}He crawls from bowls of cold soup
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去偷浪费东西的小孩的梦\N{\fs38}to steal the dreams of wasteful children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要真是那样你可是走运了\N{\fs38}That'd be a lucky break for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动 直接射杀\N{\fs38}Go, shoot to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把他拿下了\N{\fs38}We got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为本腌黄瓜\N{\fs38}Because this pickle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不在乎你的孩子们\N{\fs38}doesn’t care about your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我让他们失去的不是梦\N{\fs38}And I’m not gonna take their dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们的父母\N{\fs38}I’m gonna take their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Solen'ya 他来了\N{\fs38}Solen ‘ya! He’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我把我吃了一半的三明治扔了\N{\fs38}It’s because I threw halfway my sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是一根腌黄瓜\N{\fs38}He’s just a pickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个怪物\N{\fs38}He’s a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是唯一的一个\N{\fs38}He’s not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以待在这 不问世事直到死在这个房间里\N{\fs38}You can stay dead to the world and die in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者为我杀掉一根腌黄瓜来重获自由\N{\fs38}Or you can kill a pickle for me and earn your freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你的领袖还有一口气在 就没有自由可言\N{\fs38}There is no freedom while your leader breathes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的国家就是一座监狱\N{\fs38}Our country is a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么Catarina就是个囚犯\N{\fs38}Then Catarina is a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我也能安排她逃走\N{\fs38}Perhaps I could arrange her escape, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还活着 Jaguar\N{\fs38}She lives, Jaguar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那根腌黄瓜在哪\N{\fs38}Where is this pickle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为注射器里是什么 Beth\N{\fs38}What do you think is in the syringe, Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那个每小时收两百美元的人 你来告诉我\N{\fs38}You’re the one that costs $200 an hour. You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗腌黄瓜血清 - 是抗腌黄瓜血清\N{\fs38}Anti-pickle serum. -It’s anti-pickle serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的孩子们认为可能是抗腌黄瓜血清\N{\fs38}Your kids think it might be anti-pickle serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子尿在书桌上 吸没烧过的花瓶\N{\fs38}My kids pee their desks and suck on unbaked vases.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只是气我和他们的父亲离婚\N{\fs38}They’re just angry at me for divorcing their father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没说过我生你的气\N{\fs38}I never said I was angry at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才会吸珐琅 Summer\N{\fs38}That’s the point of pottery-enamel huffing, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样做是为了不用把\N{\fs38}You do it so you don’t have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我生你的气 妈妈"大声说出来\N{\fs38}“I’m angry at Mommy,” out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的天啊 哦 这\N{\fs38}Oh, my God! Oh, there --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有人吃屎的照片\N{\fs38}there’s pictures of people eating poop in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表明立场或者做出批判并不是我的工作\N{\fs38}It’s not my job to take sides or pass judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为当你的父亲向你要注射器的时候\N{\fs38}Do you think when your father asks for that syringe,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以问他 - 他没必要问我要 好吗\N{\fs38}you could ask him. - He won’t have to ask for it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不需要\N{\fs38}He won’t need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只用再造就好了\N{\fs38}He’ll just make more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不需要问任何人要任何东西\N{\fs38}He doesn’t need anything from anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很崇拜他这一点\N{\fs38}You admire him for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这总比把你自己的问题\N{\fs38}It’s better than making your problems
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成别人的问题要好\N{\fs38}other people’s problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 该死\N{\fs38}Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌黄瓜人 你应该知道这不是私人恩怨\N{\fs38}Pickle Man, you should know this isn’t personal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该知道这句话多没新意\N{\fs38}You should know that isn’t original.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们抓走了我的女儿\N{\fs38}They have my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了再次见到她我愿意做任何事\N{\fs38}There’s nothing I won’t do to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 为了见我女儿很多事我不会做\N{\fs38}Yeah, there’s lots I wouldn’t do to see my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是杀死你能让我快些见到她\N{\fs38}but killing you gets me to her quicker
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是听你毫无创意的屁话\N{\fs38}than your derivative bulishit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不说屁话 腌黄瓜人\N{\fs38}I never bulishit, Pickle Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们中的一个死了才能有个了结\N{\fs38}This can only end with one of us dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我从没死过\N{\fs38}and I have never died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就要死在这上面了 Jaguar\N{\fs38}That will be your downfall, Jaguar,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿接受新的经历\N{\fs38}not being open to new experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定了吗\N{\fs38}Is it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jaguar\N{\fs38}Jaguar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jaguar失败了\N{\fs38}Jaguar couldn’t make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\fs38}PAVEL: Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢了 腌黄瓜人\N{\fs38}Okay, you win, Pickle Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就把这幢楼解封\N{\fs38}I’m unsealing the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 谢谢 我来找你了\N{\fs38}No, thanks. I’m coming for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌黄瓜人 二楼的保险箱里\N{\fs38}Pickle Man, there’s $100 million worth of bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有价值一亿美元的债券\N{\fs38}in a safe on level two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把密码告诉你\N{\fs38}Ill give you the combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些钱属于人民\N{\fs38}That money belongs to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴蠢货 给我叫直升机\N{\fs38}Shut up and call me a helicopter, you prick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成交吗\N{\fs38}Do we have a deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那钱给Jaguar的女儿\N{\fs38}Take that money, give it to Jaguar’s daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她放了\N{\fs38}when you set her free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我不会放过你\N{\fs38}Or I’ll be visiting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jaguar的女儿已经死了\N{\fs38}PAVEL: Jaguar’s daughter is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你是骗子\N{\fs38}Huh, so you’re a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jaguar是头野兽\N{\fs38}PAVEL: Jaguar was an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你是根聪明的腌黄瓜\N{\fs38}You’re an intelligent pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个能谈生意\N{\fs38}We can do business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不行 一会儿见\N{\fs38}I don’t think so. See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直升机到了吗 - 到了\N{\fs38}Is the helicopter here? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察也在路上了\N{\fs38}And the police are on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么跟他们说\N{\fs38}What do we tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊\N{\fs38}-Ooh! -Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他们说我们被抢了\N{\fs38}Tell them we were robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你在干什么呢\N{\fs38}Hey! Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这儿\N{\fs38}I’m right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 Solen'ya\N{\fs38}Farewell, Solen’ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F-15战斗机出动了\N{\fs38}F-15s are scrambled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架直升机七分钟之内会被击毁\N{\fs38}This helicopter will be shot down in seven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我五分钟后能见到我女儿\N{\fs38}Well, my daughter is about five away,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有八分钟可以活\N{\fs38}and I’ve got about eight to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腌黄瓜人 我已经来不及和女儿说\N{\fs38}Pickle Man, it’s too late for me to tell my daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱她了 但你可以\N{\fs38}I love her, but not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 没事 她知道的\N{\fs38}Oh, well, uh, she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不相信那种废话\N{\fs38}I mean, we don’t really buy into that kind of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果爱是表达慢慢建立的熟悉感\N{\fs38}To the extent that love is an expression of familiarity over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那向我敞开的无尽的时间线\N{\fs38}my access to infinite timelines
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得建立情感依赖根本没有必要\N{\fs38}precludes the necessity of attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至在某个地球上\N{\fs38}In fact, I even abandoned one of my infinite daughters
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛弃了我无数多女儿中的一个\N{\fs38}in an alternate version of earth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个地球全是变异体\N{\fs38}that was taken over by mutants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 祝你好运\N{\fs38}Okay. Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我有没有无数多个女儿\N{\fs38}Wait. Do I have infinite daughters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 不好意思\N{\fs38}Huh? Uh, no. No, nope, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我有\N{\fs38}Nope, just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈呀\N{\fs38}Yeesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs38}I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担\N{\fs38}am...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心\N{\fs38}afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子们会被开除\N{\fs38}that my kids will get expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 Summer 轮到你\N{\fs38}Good. Summer, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很不爽\N{\fs38}I am mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都觉得我吸珐琅\N{\fs38}that I can’t huff enamel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我的家庭有问题\N{\fs38}without people assuming it’s because my family sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望有一天 在大家眼中\N{\fs38}I hope to be seen one day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是个单纯喜欢嗨的人\N{\fs38}as someone that just likes getting high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs38}Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你要来说说"我"的宣言吗\N{\fs38}Morty, do you have an “I” statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为\N{\fs38}I am sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尿尿难过\N{\fs38}that I peed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为我在课堂上而不是在厕所里尿尿感到难过\N{\fs38}I’m sad that I peed in class instead of a toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这一家子 你们真棒\N{\fs38}Look at this family go. You guys are pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们觉得每周进行一次心理咨询怎么样\N{\fs38}What do you guys think about doing this once a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃\N{\fs38}Ugh..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必你就是Rick - 没错\N{\fs38}You must be Rick. -Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天听了很多关于你的事\N{\fs38}I’ve heard a lot about you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的家人都对你很上心\N{\fs38}Your family is crazy about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对于你女儿来说很重要\N{\fs38}Your daughter holds you in very high regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个幸运的人\N{\fs38}You’re a lucky fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 谢谢\N{\fs38}Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 亲爱的\N{\fs38}Uh, sweetie,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你包里不会碰巧还装着那个注射器吧\N{\fs38}you don’t still happen to have that syringe in your purse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fs38}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能告诉我注射器里是什么\N{\fs38}I would like you to tell me what’s in the syringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种我 呃 赖以存活的血清\N{\fs38}It's a serum that I need to, uh -- to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天诸事不顺\N{\fs38}I have had a rough day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 呃 我还身负重伤\N{\fs38}And, uh, I’ve sustained a lot of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我濒临死亡 这管血清能救活我\N{\fs38}I’m pretty close to death, which the serum will prevent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过让你从腌黄瓜变回人类\N{\fs38}By changing you from a pickle to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs38}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你为什么要骗你女儿呢\N{\fs38}Rick, why did you lie to your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就不用来这儿\N{\fs38}So I wouldn’t have to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不愿意来这儿呢\N{\fs38}Why didn’t you want to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我看不起心理咨询 因为我是个科学家\N{\fs38}Because I don’t respect therapy, because I’m a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我以发明 改造 创造 和毁灭为生\N{\fs38}Because I invent, transform, create, and destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我不喜欢这个世界的某些部分\N{\fs38}for a living, and when I don’t like something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去改变它\N{\fs38}about the world, I change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不认为 到一个商业街里租来的办公室来\N{\fs38}And I don’t think going to a rented office in a strip mall
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听一个典型的平庸之辈\N{\fs38}to listen to some agent of averageness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我解释哪个词表达哪种感受\N{\fs38}explain which words mean which feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以解决问题\N{\fs38}has ever helped anyone do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这能让很多人安心\N{\fs38}I think it’s helped a lot of people get comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且不再恐慌 这是一种\N{\fs38}and sTop panicking, which is a state of mind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待宰动物才需要的心态\N{\fs38}we value in the animals we eat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我想要的\N{\fs38}but not something I want for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是头牛\N{\fs38}I’m not a cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个腌黄瓜 只要我愿意我就是\N{\fs38}I’m a pickle -- when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 这就是你要的答案\N{\fs38}So...you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你无可置疑的智识\N{\fs38}Rick, the only connection between
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与破坏你家庭的疾病之间的唯一联系\N{\fs38}your unquestionable intelligence and the sickness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你家庭中的所有人\N{\fs38}destroying your family is that everyone in your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括你 都用智识证明这种病态是合理的\N{\fs38}you included, use intelligence to justify sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎时而认为你的心智\N{\fs38}You seem to alternate between viewing your own mind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一种无法阻挡的力量 又认为它是一种无法避免的诅咒\N{\fs38}as an unsToppable force and as an inescapable curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得那是因为 对你而言\N{\fs38}And I think it’s because the only
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一真正难以理解的概念\N{\fs38}truly unapproachable concept for you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是掌控自己的心智\N{\fs38}is that it’s your mind within your control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你选择来到这里\N{\fs38}You chose to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也选择用谈话来贬低我的职业\N{\fs38}You chose to talk, to belittle my vocation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,—如你选择成为一个腌黄瓜\N{\fs38}just as you chose to become a pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是你自己宇宙中的主宰\N{\fs38}You are the master of your universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你却浑身滴着老鼠血和排泄物\N{\fs38}and yet you are dripping with rat blood and feces,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你强大的心智因你自己像真正的植物一样无力\N{\fs38}your enormous mind literally vegetating by your own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点不怀疑你会无意识地对心理咨询感到厌烦\N{\fs38}I have no doubt that you would be bored senseless
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同我在刷牙和擦屁股时\N{\fs38}by therapy, the same way I’m bored when I brush my teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到厌烦一样\N{\fs38}and wipe my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为修补\N{\fs38}Because the thing about repairing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持和清理这些事都不是冒险\N{\fs38}maintaining, and cleaning is it’s not an adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这些事就算犯再大的错也不至死\N{\fs38}There’s no way to do it so wrong, you might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是工作罢了\N{\fs38}It’s just work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而结果是\N{\fs38}And the bottom line is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人觉得去工作挺好 而有些人\N{\fs38}some people are okay going to work, and some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人宁愿去死\N{\fs38}well, some people would rather die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每个人都可以选择\N{\fs38}Each of us gets to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间到了\N{\fs38}That’s our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你们我的名片\N{\fs38}I’m going to give you guys my card
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待你们的消息\N{\fs38}and hope to hear from you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们有任何吃大便的朋友亲戚\N{\fs38}And if you have any friends or family that eat poop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且想要停止的话 给他们我的号码\N{\fs38}and would like to sTop, give them my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs38}I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思为了脱身我撒谎了\N{\fs38}I’m sorry I lied to get out of the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不该对你撒谎的\N{\fs38}-I -- I shouldn’t lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs38}Oh, it’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 不过没错 你不该撒谎\N{\fs38}I mean, thank you, and, yeah, you shouldn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我希望你明白这次咨询\N{\fs38}But I hope you know that’s not what
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本不该是这样的\N{\fs38}that session was supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我知道是有关Morty尿裤子\N{\fs38}Oh, no, I mean, I know it was Morty peeing his pants
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer吸胶还是什么事的\N{\fs38}and Summer snorting glue or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她吸了珐琅 我们竟然从来没谈过这事\N{\fs38}She huffed enamel, and we never even talked about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那么多要紧事呢\N{\fs38}RICK: Well, there was so much more at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那心理医生 真能说\N{\fs38}RICK: I mean, that shrink, what a monologuist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以后还会去吗\N{\fs38}Are we gonna go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝 能给我那个注射器了吗\N{\fs38}Sweetie, could I get -- get that syringe now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 当然能了爸 它在我包里\N{\fs38}Oh, my God, yes! Dad, it’s in my purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思 你一定很痛苦\N{\fs38}Oh, I’m sorry. You must be in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎\N{\fs38}Eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs38}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天啊 这些个心理咨询师\N{\fs38}Jesus Christ. Therapists, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪胎一堆\N{\fs38}Weird breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真怀念有手臂\N{\fs38}Man, I missed having hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有血还有胃\N{\fs38}and blood and a stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该喝一杯\N{\fs38}We should get a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 找个地方喝一杯\N{\fs38}Really? Like, go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 把孩子们送下车 去喝个酩酊大醉\N{\fs38}Yeah, let’s drop the kids off and go tie one on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妥妥的\N{\fs38}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我挺喜欢她的\N{\fs38}I-I liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你怎么想 去斯莫奇酒馆\N{\fs38}So what are you thinking, like, Smokey’s Tavern?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者肖尼斯\N{\fs38}Maybe Shoney’s?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个都行 哪个都行\N{\fs38}Yeah, either one. Either one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能逍遥法外的 协奏怪人\N{\fs38}RICK: You’ll never get away with this, Concerto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你所犯的错了 Sanchez先生\N{\fs38}That is where you’re mistaken, Mr. Sanchez.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这将是我有史以来最精彩的演出\N{\fs38}This shall be my greatest performance of all time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:22:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 Morty 我们死定了\N{\fs38}RICK: This is it, Morty. We’re goners.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们逃不掉了\N{\fs38}We’re not getting out of this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起经历了那么多\N{\fs38}After everything we’ve been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就要这么死掉了\N{\fs38}this is how we’re gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向神祈求安息吧\N{\fs38}Make peace with your god.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Rick 我我我不想死\N{\fs38}Oh, geez, Rick, I-I-I don’t want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 最后一砸\N{\fs38}And now for the E-splat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jaguar\N{\fs38}Jaguar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁 那是谁啊 Rick\N{\fs38}Who -- Who was that, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是为什么别去心理咨询\N{\fs38}That, Morty, is why you don’t go to therapy.
